title: Gross Private Domestic Investment Change in Business Inventories for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1921-1939 (2)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1939-1968. Unadjusted Figures Were Multiplied By Four To Derive Totals At Annual Rates.
